GET http://localhost:3000/projetos/999/tarefas

# ==========================================
# Outras Operações
# ==========================================

### PATCH - Atualizar tarefa
PATCH http://localhost:3000/tarefas/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "concluida"
}

### PATCH - Concluir/Desconcluir tarefa
PATCH http://localhost:3000/tarefas/1/concluir

### DELETE - Remover tarefa
DELETE http://localhost:3000/tarefas/1

### PATCH - Atualizar projeto
PATCH http://localhost:3000/projetos/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "descricao": "API REST e autenticação"
}

### DELETE - Remover projeto (cascata delete)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/projetos/3
